# VoteWise AI Environment Variables

# 1. Get your free API keys from Google AI Studio (Gemini)
# https://aistudio.google.com/
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=

# 2. Get keys from Google Cloud Console (Maps + Calendar)
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_maps_api_key_here
VITE_GOOGLE_CALENDAR_API_KEY=your_calendar_api_key_here

# Note: In the current lightweight prototype, you can simply paste your Gemini API key directly into the UI modal when prompted!
